import React from "react";
import {Grid, Paper} from "@material-ui/core";

export default props => <Grid container>
    <Grid item sm>
        <Paper style={{padding: 20}}>
            Left Pane
        </Paper>
    </Grid>
    <Grid item sm>
        <Paper>
            Right Pane
        </Paper>
    </Grid>
</Grid>
